- Fixed bugs related to autosave behavior:
    - Ensure countdown pauses to prevent saving page while typing in notes
    - Ensure cursor is returned to note area if that was its position prior to save.
    - Return scroll to its posiiton prior to save.
- Minor changes to menu bar appearance across multipel pages.
- Added button to return to binder from group management screen.
        </div>
        <hr style="border-top: 1px solid dimgray;" />



