- Group Changes:
    - Fixed bug that allowed text to be added to a group multiple times.
    - Fixed bug that removed group from text when new vision is created.
    - Added group information to Edit and View text screens.
    - Added ability to add/remove text from groups from the Edit text screen.
- Added notes to the search feature.
        </div>
