    -Will be saved and track across revisions.
    -Note history is not saved/archived the way Texts are, and previous versions will not be visible
- Add ability for user to specify time zone, and for that time zone to accurately reflect the create/update timestamps
- Change behavior so text edit screen redirects to view after a specified timeout period
- Adjust Autosave key-up timer from 5 seconds to 15
</div>
